### Show All Rows

For small tables where every row matters, set `show_all=True` to disable the head/tail split
entirely:

::: {#4164a998 .cell execution_count=15}
``` {.python .cell-code}
tbl_preview(
    {"name": ["Alice", "Bob", "Charlie"], "score": [95, 82, 71]},
    show_all=True,
)
```

