## Display Options

Every visual element of the preview table can be toggled on or off independently. This lets you
create anything from a fully-featured data preview to a minimal, stripped-down table.

### Captions

Add a descriptive caption that appears below the header banner and above the column labels:

::: {#0da7bae7 .cell execution_count=19}
``` {.python .cell-code}
tbl_preview(
    {"city": ["Tokyo", "Paris", "New York"], "population": [13960000, 2161000, 8336000]},
    show_all=True,
    caption="World cities by population (2024 estimates)",
)
```

